This repository is for translating the Bible into Lojban. The files are 
in USFM. The history contains the edits in Texinfo. This repo does not 
contain all the translations of the Bible into Lojban that have been 
done, as of the initial commit; please add the others. For write 
permission, ask Pierre.

https://github.com/phma/lojban-bible/blob/master/Matthew.usfm